1
00:02:41,892 --> 00:02:45,089
The path of life

2
00:02:45,362 --> 00:02:48,854
Are dreams, like the length of the path

3
00:02:49,766 --> 00:02:52,462
The storm on the way

4
00:02:52,669 --> 00:02:57,163
Pass by as you go along

5
00:02:57,608 --> 00:03:00,702
ln the world

6
00:03:01,044 --> 00:03:04,639
How many ways can one dream?

7
00:03:05,249 --> 00:03:09,948
Looking for dream-like love

8
00:03:10,354 --> 00:03:14,848
And the path goes on

9
00:03:15,359 --> 00:03:18,351
Life is what

10
00:03:18,695 --> 00:03:22,495
Dreams and desires are made of

11
00:03:23,100 --> 00:03:25,898
Somewhere in the dream

12
00:03:26,103 --> 00:03:30,199
There are traces of tears

13
00:03:30,941 --> 00:03:33,933
Where to go to?

14
00:03:34,378 --> 00:03:37,870
To find where my heart wants to go

15
00:03:38,615 --> 00:03:43,314
The wind seems to sign in the dream,

16
00:03:43,687 --> 00:03:47,384
And the path and l go on

17
00:04:20,691 --> 00:04:23,387
lt suddenly rains and suddenly shines

18
00:04:24,394 --> 00:04:26,089
Please have a pity on us travellers!

19
00:04:42,679 --> 00:04:44,579
Stop!

20
00:04:45,182 --> 00:04:46,376
Run!

21
00:04:54,091 --> 00:04:56,389
Have mercy, sir! Take it back!

22
00:04:56,627 --> 00:04:58,618
How dare you steal my money? Damn you!

23
00:05:57,788 --> 00:05:58,686
Stop! Stop!

24
00:05:58,822 --> 00:06:00,221
ls it wanted convict?

25
00:06:06,663 --> 00:06:08,961
Go away!...

26
00:06:13,136 --> 00:06:14,626
Stop! Stop!

27
00:06:15,439 --> 00:06:16,838
ls it him?

28
00:06:17,274 --> 00:06:18,468
Doesn't look like him! Go.

29
00:06:24,881 --> 00:06:25,973
Thank you!

30
00:06:27,784 --> 00:06:29,183
Don't go!

31
00:06:34,424 --> 00:06:35,721
lf you are not wanted, stay away!

32
00:06:35,859 --> 00:06:37,850
Stay away, go!

33
00:06:38,829 --> 00:06:40,023
Stop!

34
00:06:42,532 --> 00:06:43,328
Not him!

35
00:06:43,500 --> 00:06:44,398
Tell him to leave!

36
00:06:44,868 --> 00:06:46,165
Stop!

37
00:06:50,741 --> 00:06:51,639
Stop!

38
00:06:51,808 --> 00:06:52,604
Who's screaming?

39
00:06:52,743 --> 00:06:53,641
Over there!

40
00:06:53,977 --> 00:06:55,069
Stop!

41
00:06:55,278 --> 00:06:56,370
Stop!

42
00:06:56,446 --> 00:06:57,538
There's a wanted convict!

43
00:06:58,982 --> 00:07:01,177
Who told you to stop?

44
00:07:04,588 --> 00:07:05,987
Pilgrimage? How hilarious!

45
00:07:07,157 --> 00:07:08,749
You have all my money!

46
00:07:08,859 --> 00:07:09,655
Don't advantage from me!

47
00:07:09,793 --> 00:07:11,988
Don't say that, l don't need it!

48
00:07:12,162 --> 00:07:13,561
You may need it sooner or later!

49
00:07:14,865 --> 00:07:16,059
Thank you!

50
00:07:16,800 --> 00:07:18,199
Want a room, Sir?

51
00:07:18,368 --> 00:07:19,767
Get the luggage for him.

52
00:07:19,936 --> 00:07:20,925
There's a nice room.

53
00:07:21,138 --> 00:07:23,129
Sorry, but l'm a collector
from Tsi Pao Chu.

54
00:07:23,640 --> 00:07:24,629
Collector?

55
00:07:25,776 --> 00:07:27,175
Without rules!

56
00:07:27,544 --> 00:07:28,943
Why is it a different man each time?

57
00:07:29,146 --> 00:07:30,443
The ex-collector was killed
on his way home.

58
00:07:30,514 --> 00:07:32,414
Why don't you just do me a favour.

59
00:07:32,549 --> 00:07:34,039
Since you might get killed
with the money?

60
00:07:34,117 --> 00:07:35,106
Stop collecting.

61
00:07:35,218 --> 00:07:36,913
You must be joking.

62
00:07:44,194 --> 00:07:47,789
Can't see the counterfoll?
lt's the new rules.

63
00:07:48,131 --> 00:07:50,122
New rule? Show me!

64
00:07:50,267 --> 00:07:51,359
Sorry, no!

65
00:07:51,468 --> 00:07:52,662
What kind of a record is that?

66
00:07:52,869 --> 00:07:54,962
lt's in such a mess.

67
00:07:55,205 --> 00:07:57,503
l can't return without the collection.

68
00:07:57,574 --> 00:07:58,666
Sorry to bother you.

69
00:07:59,709 --> 00:08:01,108
l owe you nothing.

70
00:08:01,278 --> 00:08:02,575
You book shows it.

71
00:08:02,712 --> 00:08:05,510
Don't deny it or l'll take
you to court.

72
00:08:14,224 --> 00:08:16,624
lnn keeper, where can l
spend a night without paying

73
00:08:16,893 --> 00:08:19,794
Go to the Lan Ro Temple!

74
00:08:27,103 --> 00:08:29,003
Old lady, l didn't lie to you.

75
00:08:29,139 --> 00:08:30,834
Where's Lan Ro Temple, please?

76
00:08:31,641 --> 00:08:35,634
Lan Ro Temple?! 3 1/2 miles
to the East.

77
00:08:35,779 --> 00:08:37,974
Where there is a spocky temple!

78
00:08:40,350 --> 00:08:41,146
Thank you!

79
00:08:45,889 --> 00:08:47,083
Sorry! Excuse me!

80
00:08:49,726 --> 00:08:51,523
Old lady, are you going
to buy it or not?

81
00:09:08,645 --> 00:09:10,044
Well done!

82
00:09:11,548 --> 00:09:15,143
Master, you've good taste,
make an offer!

83
00:09:15,485 --> 00:09:18,181
l don't even have money
for travel expenses.

84
00:09:20,023 --> 00:09:22,924
Good taste, but no means,
what's the use?

85
00:09:23,293 --> 00:09:24,487
What are you doing?

86
00:09:24,628 --> 00:09:26,823
l'm taking your measurement
for your coffin!

87
00:09:27,030 --> 00:09:27,826
Thank you!

88
00:09:27,964 --> 00:09:31,559
Remember, there are wolves
in the woods.

89
00:09:31,768 --> 00:09:33,565
You may come upon them
when it's dark.

90
00:09:34,204 --> 00:09:35,193
Stop...

91
00:10:23,687 --> 00:10:24,676
The fire cannot go out.

92
00:10:24,788 --> 00:10:25,982
lf it does, l can't get out
of the forest.

93
00:10:33,763 --> 00:10:35,856
Lan Ro Temple.

94
00:10:49,112 --> 00:10:50,204
Anybody in?

95
00:12:05,689 --> 00:12:06,986
Have you finished?

96
00:12:07,123 --> 00:12:11,116
Hsia-hou, we're fought for
7 years & you're always lost

97
00:12:11,795 --> 00:12:13,387
But you're quite persevering

98
00:12:13,697 --> 00:12:15,494
You follow me wherever l go.

99
00:12:16,199 --> 00:12:18,497
You've been in the Temple
for a fornight

100
00:12:18,702 --> 00:12:20,602
and you've improved your
swordsmanship!

101
00:12:20,737 --> 00:12:23,137
But you've wasted your youth too.

102
00:12:23,673 --> 00:12:26,369
You're ambitious, but not aggressive.

103
00:12:26,976 --> 00:12:30,776
For the sake of the title,
you've become biased

104
00:12:31,181 --> 00:12:33,581
You're petulant but not
concentrated enough.

105
00:12:33,817 --> 00:12:35,307
Your blows are violent but
ineffective.

106
00:12:38,021 --> 00:12:40,717
You've to cool down if not
you can win lust.

107
00:12:40,957 --> 00:12:42,549
l'm here to duel with you,

108
00:12:42,859 --> 00:12:44,759
not to listen to your sermon

109
00:12:44,928 --> 00:12:47,419
Yes, he's right!

110
00:12:47,630 --> 00:12:50,827
He's not your match. You
shouldn't have

111
00:12:51,034 --> 00:12:52,228
said that to disgrace him.

112
00:12:53,169 --> 00:12:55,467
He's right too.

113
00:12:55,705 --> 00:12:56,797
You shouldn't have followed
him.

114
00:12:57,273 --> 00:13:00,674
Lay down your swords &
touch him with love.

115
00:13:00,844 --> 00:13:03,335
The universe is limitless
& love is eternal.

116
00:13:03,513 --> 00:13:07,210
Love conquers the world.

117
00:13:07,484 --> 00:13:09,281
Love is the most powerful weapon!

118
00:13:13,323 --> 00:13:14,312
Because you said too much!

119
00:13:16,626 --> 00:13:17,615
l'm not trying to follow you

120
00:13:22,766 --> 00:13:23,562
Your clothing is torn.

121
00:13:23,733 --> 00:13:24,631
Hell with your love!

122
00:13:24,901 --> 00:13:26,198
The kind of love you need,

123
00:13:26,336 --> 00:13:27,530
you should find in a
whorehouse.

124
00:13:28,071 --> 00:13:29,060
l'm trying to find a place.

125
00:13:29,205 --> 00:13:30,103
lt's not convenient!

126
00:13:30,974 --> 00:13:31,770
Why not?

127
00:13:32,742 --> 00:13:33,731
Are you bold or not?

128
00:13:33,843 --> 00:13:34,741
Yes!

129
00:13:35,078 --> 00:13:35,976
Look over there!

130
00:13:39,916 --> 00:13:42,407
l just shout, you then hide up.

131
00:13:42,685 --> 00:13:43,982
lf there's a real tiger

132
00:13:44,187 --> 00:13:45,779
Where should you hide?

133
00:13:46,756 --> 00:13:47,950
What? lt really has a tiger?

134
00:13:48,992 --> 00:13:49,890
No!

135
00:13:50,660 --> 00:13:52,355
But we've something even
more scareful than a tiger.

136
00:13:53,263 --> 00:13:54,855
Do you always keep so close
while talking?

137
00:13:55,098 --> 00:13:57,589
l've had breath, & this will
keep you away.

138
00:13:58,902 --> 00:13:59,994
Get out of here!

139
00:14:00,436 --> 00:14:02,028
Your love can't save you.

140
00:14:02,639 --> 00:14:03,731
Yes!

141
00:14:03,840 --> 00:14:04,636
Me too!

142
00:17:33,249 --> 00:17:36,150
Hsia-hou, you're ambitious but,

143
00:17:36,285 --> 00:17:39,686
after death, you're still a nobody.

144
00:17:41,891 --> 00:17:43,984
l won't expose your body
in the wilderness.

145
00:17:49,999 --> 00:17:52,297
You never change, you fight
even when dead.

146
00:17:55,905 --> 00:17:56,997
Pao-Yeh-Pao-Lo-Mi!

147
00:19:31,934 --> 00:19:33,128
lt's lucky that water isn't deep.

148
00:19:33,569 --> 00:19:34,968
Otherwise l'll get wet.

149
00:20:00,229 --> 00:20:01,628
That monster's out again!

150
00:20:01,898 --> 00:20:03,798
Shit! ls he still be there?

151
00:20:19,715 --> 00:20:21,808
l meant no harm.

152
00:20:22,051 --> 00:20:23,348
l'll throw it away if you're afraid!

153
00:20:35,498 --> 00:20:36,487
What's it?

154
00:20:39,402 --> 00:20:40,391
Where's my veil?

155
00:20:41,837 --> 00:20:42,633
Veil? l'll find up for you!

156
00:20:46,842 --> 00:20:48,036
lt's deep!

157
00:20:50,613 --> 00:20:52,706
Come up quick!

158
00:20:53,883 --> 00:20:54,872
Come up!

159
00:20:56,385 --> 00:20:57,181
Thank you!

160
00:20:58,721 --> 00:21:00,313
lt's too dark, l can't see.

161
00:21:00,990 --> 00:21:02,389
l'll find it up early tomorrow.

162
00:21:06,429 --> 00:21:07,521
This water is both deep and cold!

163
00:21:09,465 --> 00:21:11,456
Your hand are colder than mine.

164
00:21:11,634 --> 00:21:12,931
Because you're warmer.

165
00:21:16,372 --> 00:21:19,569
You're sick, you look so pale.

166
00:21:20,176 --> 00:21:21,575
Go to see doctor.

167
00:21:22,111 --> 00:21:24,306
l need your warmth.

168
00:21:26,449 --> 00:21:27,643
l'm not willing to push you.

169
00:21:27,750 --> 00:21:29,741
lf not, l'll spit on you.

170
00:21:30,019 --> 00:21:31,213
lt hurts.

171
00:21:35,758 --> 00:21:36,952
l shouldn't have pushed you.

172
00:21:37,059 --> 00:21:38,151
lt's cold.

173
00:21:39,262 --> 00:21:41,253
l'm wet, you'll feel colder
lying on me.

174
00:21:43,266 --> 00:21:44,062
Do you feel painful or cold?

175
00:21:44,200 --> 00:21:45,599
Hold me and take me inside.

176
00:21:45,901 --> 00:21:46,799
Holding you?

177
00:21:49,305 --> 00:21:51,296
l can't, you're too heavy!

178
00:21:53,476 --> 00:21:55,467
l need some help...

179
00:22:03,819 --> 00:22:08,222
You look nice, but you're
in the wrong place.

180
00:22:09,492 --> 00:22:11,687
Otherwise, you wouldn't have
died for nothing.

181
00:22:19,835 --> 00:22:21,029
Why am l still in water?

182
00:22:28,244 --> 00:22:29,836
Miss, you forgot your lute!

183
00:23:12,221 --> 00:23:13,313
Why are you following me?

184
00:23:19,295 --> 00:23:20,193
Why are you leaving?

185
00:23:20,329 --> 00:23:22,229
A villain! l must run for my life!

186
00:23:22,498 --> 00:23:24,898
Who? l can't see it!

187
00:23:59,034 --> 00:24:01,935
Stepping you to death.

188
00:24:02,104 --> 00:24:03,503
Let's go.

189
00:24:04,340 --> 00:24:05,432
Snake!

190
00:24:14,417 --> 00:24:15,509
Where's the snake?

191
00:24:16,752 --> 00:24:17,946
Don't shout!

192
00:24:18,788 --> 00:24:20,380
The villain just passes by.

193
00:24:21,757 --> 00:24:22,746
Which one?

194
00:24:23,092 --> 00:24:24,889
The bearded one on the East
of Lan Ro Temple.

195
00:24:25,094 --> 00:24:26,789
lf he discovered us, we'd be killed!

196
00:24:28,597 --> 00:24:29,996
The one living opposite me?

197
00:24:31,066 --> 00:24:33,261
l could tell that he no good

198
00:24:36,906 --> 00:24:38,703
You're too dangerous! On
your own l'll take you back.

199
00:24:38,941 --> 00:24:41,136
No, my family won't permit this.

200
00:24:41,343 --> 00:24:42,139
They're very strict.

201
00:24:42,244 --> 00:24:44,041
Miss,

202
00:24:44,213 --> 00:24:45,111
let me lure him away then!

203
00:24:45,448 --> 00:24:47,143
Run when he tries to get
hold of me!

204
00:24:49,351 --> 00:24:51,444
Don't let him sees you.

205
00:24:55,858 --> 00:24:58,258
Here's you lute, Miss!

206
00:25:07,436 --> 00:25:08,528
What's your name?

207
00:25:08,971 --> 00:25:09,869
Ning Tsai-shen!

208
00:25:13,609 --> 00:25:14,507
What's yours?

209
00:25:14,810 --> 00:25:15,902
Nieh Hsiao Tsing!

210
00:25:16,846 --> 00:25:17,642
Nieh Hsiao Tsing!

211
00:25:18,314 --> 00:25:19,804
Tomorrow night...

212
00:25:22,017 --> 00:25:23,416
Tomorrow night l'll come
to see you.

213
00:26:31,720 --> 00:26:32,812
Stop running!

214
00:26:34,223 --> 00:26:35,315
lt's dangerous.

215
00:26:46,835 --> 00:26:47,927
Stop! You can't get away!

216
00:27:03,819 --> 00:27:07,311
lf you think you can scream,
l can scream too!

217
00:27:07,456 --> 00:27:10,948
Damn Taoist, both of us want
shelter here.

218
00:27:11,327 --> 00:27:13,022
Actually, all the men l
killed deserve it.

219
00:27:13,362 --> 00:27:15,262
Why have you been annoying me?

220
00:27:15,898 --> 00:27:17,889
l'm not.

221
00:27:18,667 --> 00:27:19,964
l'm hiding in this hellish place

222
00:27:20,369 --> 00:27:21,666
to stay away from hatred
the fighting in the world.

223
00:27:22,671 --> 00:27:25,265
We've the common objective
to annihilate criminals

224
00:27:25,407 --> 00:27:26,499
for the good of mankind.

225
00:27:26,575 --> 00:27:28,475
We're in fact are fellowmen.

226
00:27:28,544 --> 00:27:31,945
Fellowmen? Nonsense!

227
00:27:37,319 --> 00:27:38,809
You're hurting me too.

228
00:27:39,121 --> 00:27:40,713
One day, you'll be in big trouble,

229
00:27:41,023 --> 00:27:42,217
then l'll finish you off.

230
00:27:55,938 --> 00:27:57,838
You're a good man. Don't
come to me anymore.

231
00:27:58,107 --> 00:27:59,005
Hsiao Tsing!

232
00:29:03,872 --> 00:29:04,964
The big beard

233
00:29:19,088 --> 00:29:20,578
Man of love,

234
00:29:21,690 --> 00:29:24,488
Did you come upon anything
last night?

235
00:29:26,161 --> 00:29:27,651
l've touched everything in
the house.

236
00:29:28,764 --> 00:29:30,857
Did you see anything eerie?

237
00:29:32,601 --> 00:29:33,693
lncluding you?

238
00:29:38,474 --> 00:29:39,463
ldiot!

239
00:29:43,345 --> 00:29:45,745
l'm serious. Why are you joking?

240
00:29:51,386 --> 00:29:52,478
Who knows if you're

241
00:29:52,554 --> 00:29:53,543
serious or not?

242
00:29:53,756 --> 00:29:54,848
You're always joking?

243
00:29:55,157 --> 00:29:57,455
Get out of this place. lt's haunted.

244
00:29:59,094 --> 00:30:01,187
Show me the ghost if you can.

245
00:30:01,797 --> 00:30:03,788
Stupid fool. Do you think
you can see a ghost that easy?

246
00:30:04,066 --> 00:30:04,964
Then they must not be a ghost.

247
00:30:05,400 --> 00:30:07,095
They won't show up in the day.

248
00:30:07,936 --> 00:30:09,130
Big beard, don't scare me.

249
00:30:09,371 --> 00:30:11,362
Tell them to come at night,
if not in the day.

250
00:30:16,178 --> 00:30:17,270
Don't regret it.

251
00:30:17,412 --> 00:30:20,813
Why don't you believe me?

252
00:30:24,553 --> 00:30:25,952
lf l see you at night,
l'll throw you out.

253
00:30:28,257 --> 00:30:29,246
Come on, do that!

254
00:30:30,492 --> 00:30:32,687
No, l'll kill you.

255
00:30:35,964 --> 00:30:38,262
There's no better way to help him.

256
00:30:38,567 --> 00:30:39,659
Hope that can save his life.

257
00:30:41,236 --> 00:30:43,329
Ghost? He must be kidding.

258
00:30:46,508 --> 00:30:47,600
Where's my lower portion?

259
00:30:53,115 --> 00:30:55,310
Damn big beard! Where have
you put it?

260
00:30:57,186 --> 00:30:59,984
Your lower portion? lsn't it
connected to your upper portion?

261
00:31:00,589 --> 00:31:01,385
Don't talk nonsense!

262
00:31:01,523 --> 00:31:02,421
Take it!

263
00:31:02,691 --> 00:31:04,488
He's incoherent. No point
in helping him.

264
00:31:15,137 --> 00:31:17,935
lt's illegible anyway,
l'll fill it in myself.

265
00:33:15,891 --> 00:33:17,381
Have you really lived in
Lan Ro Temple?

266
00:33:17,659 --> 00:33:18,751
lt clearly shows 70 taels.

267
00:33:22,864 --> 00:33:23,762
Pay up.

268
00:33:24,900 --> 00:33:25,889
Take it.

269
00:33:28,470 --> 00:33:29,562
Thank you.

270
00:33:31,606 --> 00:33:32,504
lnn keeper!

271
00:33:32,941 --> 00:33:34,738
You scared me. What do you want?

272
00:33:36,244 --> 00:33:37,438
l was scared too.

273
00:33:38,380 --> 00:33:40,075
Excuse me, excuse me...

274
00:34:25,594 --> 00:34:26,788
Hsiao Tsing!

275
00:34:32,067 --> 00:34:32,965
