01:13:34,841 --> 01:13:36,331
l pretend to be a ghost in
front of a man,

841
01:13:37,243 --> 01:13:38,938
and a human in front of a ghost,

842
01:13:40,380 --> 01:13:41,870
and now l don't know if l'm
a man or a ghost.

843
01:13:42,682 --> 01:13:44,673
l'm not a swordsman.

844
01:13:45,017 --> 01:13:47,110
Ridiculous!

845
01:13:47,320 --> 01:13:48,412
What so funny!

846
01:13:48,788 --> 01:13:50,278
l don't want to be a man.

847
01:13:50,690 --> 01:13:52,590
But Tsing wants to reincarnation.

848
01:13:53,659 --> 01:13:55,149
Don't say that!

849
01:13:55,294 --> 01:13:57,091
The most important is to
get out here.

850
01:14:00,066 --> 01:14:02,967
l don't understand all those
nonsense!

851
01:14:03,202 --> 01:14:04,794
Alright, l promise you!

852
01:14:23,656 --> 01:14:24,748
l find it!

853
01:14:34,233 --> 01:14:35,029
Why so much?

854
01:14:35,168 --> 01:14:36,066
How strange!

855
01:14:36,235 --> 01:14:37,224
Which one?

856
01:14:37,804 --> 01:14:39,396
No time to sort out now.
Take them away!

857
01:14:43,609 --> 01:14:45,099
Where should we put the Sutra?

858
01:14:46,112 --> 01:14:46,908
ln the satchel!

859
01:14:47,079 --> 01:14:48,979
No, keep it to make the
spirits follow us.

860
01:15:03,029 --> 01:15:04,223
Follow me closely!

861
01:15:04,363 --> 01:15:05,762
l can't, you're riding too fast!

862
01:15:06,032 --> 01:15:07,829
We're in rush.

863
01:15:16,943 --> 01:15:17,739
Swordsman Yen, something wrong!

864
01:15:17,877 --> 01:15:19,174
Why are we still at the same old place?

865
01:15:19,378 --> 01:15:20,276
Must have to do with those evil spirits.

866
01:15:20,446 --> 01:15:21,344
What then?

867
01:15:21,547 --> 01:15:23,538
We must get out of the
before it's dark.

868
01:15:37,797 --> 01:15:41,893
Pao-Yeh-Pao-Lo-Mi!

869
01:15:47,440 --> 01:15:48,634
Follow me.

870
01:16:11,931 --> 01:16:13,125
Someone's celebrating!

871
01:16:13,266 --> 01:16:14,255
lnn keeper!

872
01:16:15,034 --> 01:16:16,023
Why is it deserted?

873
01:16:16,302 --> 01:16:17,291
All gone to hell!

874
01:16:18,204 --> 01:16:19,296
What?

875
01:16:19,805 --> 01:16:20,794
What are you doing?

876
01:16:20,973 --> 01:16:22,065
We want to stay the night.

877
01:16:24,210 --> 01:16:25,302
Follow me!

878
01:16:30,616 --> 01:16:31,913
You can go!

879
01:16:32,685 --> 01:16:33,879
Don't come out!

880
01:16:48,701 --> 01:16:51,101
Tsing, come out if you're
among them.

881
01:16:55,141 --> 01:17:00,238
Master, looking for me?

882
01:17:00,947 --> 01:17:05,941
Master, looking for us?

883
01:17:07,286 --> 01:17:09,686
No sign of Tsing.
Maybe the wrong ashes!

884
01:17:09,822 --> 01:17:12,620
Get back your things and vanish.

885
01:17:12,892 --> 01:17:13,984
Don't wreak havoc anymore.

886
01:17:14,126 --> 01:17:16,720
Thank you!

887
01:17:17,563 --> 01:17:18,655
Vanish.

888
01:17:21,300 --> 01:17:22,892
Last chance.

889
01:17:24,170 --> 01:17:25,364
Now this is the last.

890
01:17:25,471 --> 01:17:27,769
Tsing, come out, if it's you!

891
01:17:28,641 --> 01:17:31,542
Come out!...

892
01:17:31,744 --> 01:17:34,736
Master, looking for me?

893
01:17:38,017 --> 01:17:41,111
A male! No chance!

894
01:17:44,390 --> 01:17:46,187
Why do you keep calling me?

895
01:17:46,659 --> 01:17:47,751
lt's the waiter.

896
01:17:49,829 --> 01:17:50,921
You scare me!

897
01:17:51,063 --> 01:17:53,657
Damn! Why did you appear
so abruptly?

898
01:17:53,933 --> 01:17:54,922
Get out!

899
01:18:03,876 --> 01:18:06,674
Tsing!

900
01:18:06,746 --> 01:18:07,940
Ning Tsai-shen!

901
01:18:08,848 --> 01:18:09,940
Tsing!

902
01:18:15,755 --> 01:18:17,848
Thank you for serving my life!

903
01:18:19,959 --> 01:18:22,052
Well...! Stand up!...

904
01:18:23,062 --> 01:18:25,257
Don't be formal. We're friends.

905
01:18:28,167 --> 01:18:29,657
You're wasting the time!

906
01:18:29,869 --> 01:18:32,167
l'll replace 2 horses for
the journey tomorrow.

907
01:18:36,409 --> 01:18:38,206
What a pair of lovers!

908
01:18:41,113 --> 01:18:43,604
That's his style!

909
01:18:59,665 --> 01:19:02,361
lt's frosty all over the lake.

910
01:19:06,639 --> 01:19:12,236
Time flies like which goes grey.

911
01:19:14,880 --> 01:19:17,280
Facing the moon alone,
l need companion.

912
01:19:19,418 --> 01:19:23,013
Lovebirds fare better than fairies.

913
01:19:24,824 --> 01:19:27,019
This picture will be the
only thing l left.

914
01:19:27,326 --> 01:19:28,725
l'll keep it forever.

915
01:19:29,862 --> 01:19:32,763
We must at the town
tomorrow evening,

916
01:19:33,065 --> 01:19:35,465
if not l couldn't reincarnation.

917
01:19:37,069 --> 01:19:38,263
You should be happy for me.

918
01:19:38,771 --> 01:19:40,762
What a chance for you.

919
01:19:48,380 --> 01:19:50,177
But we must part before dawn,

920
01:19:50,316 --> 01:19:51,715
and forever.

921
01:19:54,153 --> 01:19:55,347
Heavens! Don't ever get dark

922
01:19:59,391 --> 01:20:00,585
Pao-Yeh-Pao-Lo-Mi.

923
01:20:05,197 --> 01:20:06,186
Evil in the air!

924
01:20:11,237 --> 01:20:12,431
Blood bun?

925
01:20:19,912 --> 01:20:20,810
A ghost wedding.

926
01:20:22,515 --> 01:20:25,313
Stop moping! This inn is haunted.

927
01:20:25,484 --> 01:20:26,974
Pack up and get out of here.

928
01:20:29,155 --> 01:20:30,144
l go and get the golden pagoda.

929
01:20:31,490 --> 01:20:32,479
Hurry up!

930
01:20:36,028 --> 01:20:36,824
Oh, l forgot the painting!

931
01:20:36,962 --> 01:20:37,860
Get it when day breaks.

932
01:20:38,898 --> 01:20:40,092
Ning Tsai-shen!

933
01:20:41,267 --> 01:20:42,461
Today's a good day in hell.

934
01:20:42,735 --> 01:20:44,134
They must've got Tsing back.

935
01:20:44,303 --> 01:20:45,292
Old Evil is coming to
collect the bride.

936
01:20:45,504 --> 01:20:47,995
Scholar, it seems we've
to storm hell!

937
01:20:49,275 --> 01:20:50,264
We must rescue Tsing.

938
01:20:50,409 --> 01:20:52,809
Hold it! We must rescue
her before the incense burns out.

939
01:20:52,978 --> 01:20:54,070
We can't go back when
the day breaks.

940
01:20:55,347 --> 01:20:56,336
Remember, close your eyes!

941
01:20:57,650 --> 01:20:59,447
Pao-Yeh-Pao-Lo-Mi...

942
01:21:12,364 --> 01:21:13,763
Can l open my eyes now?

943
01:21:13,833 --> 01:21:15,027
You must, if you want to find her.

944
01:21:37,723 --> 01:21:38,815
Tsing's inside.

945
01:21:39,291 --> 01:21:40,189
Tsing!

946
01:21:41,227 --> 01:21:42,216
Ning Tsai-shen!

947
01:21:42,828 --> 01:21:43,920
Tsing!

948
01:21:47,800 --> 01:21:48,994
Why can't l get hold of her?

949
01:21:49,201 --> 01:21:50,293
Ning Tsai-shen!

950
01:21:50,569 --> 01:21:52,161
Tsing...

951
01:21:52,438 --> 01:21:53,234
ln the mundane world men
can't see ghosts.

952
01:21:53,405 --> 01:21:54,599
ln hell ghosts can't see men.

953
01:21:54,773 --> 01:21:55,865
Pao-Yeh-Pao-Lo-Mi.

954
01:21:56,575 --> 01:21:58,566
Tsing can see you now. Go now.

955
01:22:08,287 --> 01:22:10,881
They're going to hell!

956
01:22:12,024 --> 01:22:13,218
Go!

957
01:22:13,659 --> 01:22:14,853
Tsing!

958
01:22:15,060 --> 01:22:16,254
What now?

959
01:22:16,362 --> 01:22:17,260
Go into hiding

960
01:22:23,769 --> 01:22:24,667
Go and rescue Tsing at once.

961
01:22:24,837 --> 01:22:25,633
Me?

962
01:22:25,704 --> 01:22:26,500
Let's go!

963
01:22:27,306 --> 01:22:28,295
Pao-Yeh-Pao-Lo-Mi.

964
01:22:30,709 --> 01:22:32,006
Heaven and earth are limitless.

965
01:22:45,124 --> 01:22:46,022
Here l am!

966
01:22:46,191 --> 01:22:47,385
Don't mind, run!

967
01:22:47,793 --> 01:22:48,782
l'm here to help you.

968
01:22:49,561 --> 01:22:50,459
l cut it for you.

969
01:22:59,038 --> 01:23:00,027
Run!

970
01:23:07,746 --> 01:23:08,838
The magic powers!

971
01:23:12,351 --> 01:23:13,545
Swordsman Yen, watch out!

972
01:23:29,368 --> 01:23:30,665
You go first, l'll stay behind.

973
01:24:09,041 --> 01:24:10,133
Find another exit.

974
01:24:35,701 --> 01:24:36,895
Pao-Yeh-Pao-Mi.

975
01:24:43,242 --> 01:24:44,038
Swordsman Yen!

976
01:24:44,209 --> 01:24:45,005
Why have you come back?

977
01:24:45,177 --> 01:24:45,973
We can't get out of here!

978
01:24:46,178 --> 01:24:46,974
Old Evil has blocked the exit.

979
01:24:49,148 --> 01:24:51,946
You can't get out of here.

980
01:24:52,551 --> 01:24:53,643
Help me get an arrow.

981
01:24:54,353 --> 01:24:55,445
Full the bow.

982
01:24:56,555 --> 01:24:57,749
Let loose!

983
01:25:01,960 --> 01:25:03,052
Bad, we're not his match.

984
01:25:12,971 --> 01:25:14,563
Pull at him. This is
1000-year old Evil.

985
01:25:14,740 --> 01:25:16,037
He may drain your soul away.

986
01:25:18,143 --> 01:25:19,132
Swordsman Yen!

987
01:25:34,660 --> 01:25:35,752
Concentrate!

988
01:25:36,095 --> 01:25:38,495
Recite! Pao-Yeh-Pao-Lo-Mi.

989
01:25:40,265 --> 01:25:42,665
Lord Black, please let them go.

990
01:25:43,802 --> 01:25:49,399
Break the golden pagoda and
be my companion.

991
01:25:49,775 --> 01:25:51,970
Tsing, don't be taken in.

992
01:25:53,245 --> 01:25:54,940
Concentrate! Recite!

993
01:25:55,848 --> 01:25:59,045
Pao-Yeh-Pao-Lo-Mi...

994
01:26:01,620 --> 01:26:02,814
Don't!

995
01:26:08,861 --> 01:26:10,055
l'll rescue you!

996
01:26:30,182 --> 01:26:31,376
Tsing!

997
01:26:37,789 --> 01:26:41,987
Yen Che-hsia, Ning Tsai-shen
l'll take your lives.

998
01:26:48,500 --> 01:26:49,489
Don't!

999
01:26:52,504 --> 01:26:56,201
What's this? The sutra?

1000
01:26:59,678 --> 01:27:00,667
You'd enough.

1001
01:27:00,746 --> 01:27:01,940
l've to get rid of your damn evil.

1002
01:27:19,431 --> 01:27:23,026
Damn old Evil!

1003
01:27:23,936 --> 01:27:25,028
Swordsman Yen!

1004
01:27:25,470 --> 01:27:27,665
The way's clear! Help
Swordsman Yen out!

1005
01:27:33,478 --> 01:27:34,570
Swordsman Yen!

1006
01:27:54,399 --> 01:27:56,697
Swordsman Yen, we're back to earth.

1007
01:27:58,136 --> 01:27:59,535
Bad, it's dawn.

1008
01:27:59,738 --> 01:28:00,830
Tsing's not yet here.

1009
01:28:01,840 --> 01:28:03,137
Help her out.

1010
01:28:10,182 --> 01:28:12,082
Swordsman Yen, lead a hand!

1011
01:28:21,126 --> 01:28:22,115
Tsing!

1012
01:28:22,828 --> 01:28:24,022
Keep her from the sunshine,

1013
01:28:24,363 --> 01:28:26,957
or she may evaporate and
can't be reincarnated.

1014
01:28:31,370 --> 01:28:34,669
Tsing, come back to the
golden pagoda!

1015
01:28:40,846 --> 01:28:44,043
The sun is rising, l've to go!

1016
01:28:47,252 --> 01:28:49,550
Tsing, be a good human being.

1017
01:28:51,423 --> 01:28:53,118
l'll remember you always.

1018
01:28:53,625 --> 01:28:56,526
Can't see you once before we apart.

1019
01:28:57,396 --> 01:28:58,385
Take care!

1020
01:29:04,503 --> 01:29:05,993
She's gone!

1021
01:29:10,442 --> 01:29:17,348
l want to be together,

1022
01:29:18,750 --> 01:29:27,249
till eternity.

1023
01:29:30,929 --> 01:29:34,729
Tsing, l'll take you back.

1024
01:30:00,392 --> 01:30:01,791
Wonder if she has been reincarnated.

1025
01:30:02,327 --> 01:30:06,627
ln there times, an unlucky man may
fare worse than a ghost.

1026
01:30:12,371 --> 01:30:13,565
Ahead.

1027
01:30:13,739 --> 01:30:14,831
Let's go.

1028
01:30:18,577 --> 01:30:21,671
The path of life

1029
01:30:22,047 --> 01:30:25,642
Are dreams, like the length of the path

1030
01:30:26,618 --> 01:30:29,519
The storm on the way

1031
01:30:29,654 --> 01:30:34,353
Pass by as you go along

1032
01:30:34,726 --> 01:30:38,127
ln the world

1033
01:30:38,196 --> 01:30:42,189
How many ways can one dream?

1034
01:30:42,667 --> 01:30:47,661
Looking for dream-like love

1035
01:30:47,873 --> 01:30:52,276
And the path goes on

1036
01:30:53,078 --> 01:31:00,177
Life is what dreams and
desires are made of

1037
01:31:00,986 --> 01:31:03,978
Somewhere in the dream

1038
01:31:04,089 --> 01:31:08,492
There are traces of tears

1039
01:31:09,127 --> 01:31:12,324
Where to go to?

1040
01:31:12,564 --> 01:31:16,364
To find where my heart wants to go

1041
01:31:16,968 --> 01:31:21,962
The wind seems to sign in the dream,

1042
01:31:22,174 --> 01:31:26,668
And the path and l go on
